creator: Horizon Ag LLC
descriptionHtml:
The Horizon Ag mobile app provides rice farmers with the latest Provisia and Clearfield seed varieties, proven to perform.

The app includes the Horizon Ag seeding rate chart, easily accessible when you’re in the field. You can use the seeding rate chart in conjunction with our drill calibration tool as you prepare to plant. If you’re not using our seeds, that’s okay, you can still use the drill calibration calculator with whichever seeds you do use. Just remember, Horizon Ag seeds are proven to perform.

Finally, we’ve also made it handy to find your local Horizon Ag seed retailer from within the app.

If you have any questions, reach out to us at info@horizonseed.com

Horizon Ag is here to provide seed and give our best advice on managing your rice crop for the highest return on investment. We hope your rice season is proven to perform!
